rows.label: tlk70000039_05_msg0001
rows.name:
I thought I would never see him again,
so to meet once more like this...it's
almost like a miracle.

rows.label: tlk70000039_05_msg0002
rows.name:
Life works in strange ways sometimes.
I'm glad I lived long enough to see
the day.

rows.label: tlk70000039_05_msg0003
rows.name:
The days when I clung to the teachings
of Acedia to escape the pain of losing
Teo feel like a distant memory now

rows.label: tlk70000039_05_msg0004
rows.name:
Perhaps this is the salvation the
teachings spoke of...?
